Request feedback or clarification on a Linear issue.

## Usage

```
/get-feedback-linear
/get-feedback-linear <brief question>
```

## Description

Use this command when you're blocked and need clarification, design input, or decisions from teammates. This command will:
- Post your questions as a comment to the Linear issue
- Update issue status to "Feedback Required" (or equivalent)
- Optionally tag specific people for visibility
- Optionally pause your work until feedback is received

Perfect for:
- Unclear requirements or acceptance criteria
- Architectural or design decisions needed
- Missing information or specifications
- UX/UI clarifications
- Product owner input required
- Technical blocker needing team discussion

