## Configuration

Uses your Linear workflow configuration:

- **Team**: {{linear.teamName}} ({{linear.teamKey}})
- **Feedback Status**: Automatically finds status with meaning "needs feedback" or "blockers"
- **Default**: If no feedback status exists, uses "On Hold"

The command intelligently maps to your workflow:
```javascript
// Find appropriate "feedback required" status
const feedbackStatus = Object.values(config.linear.statuses).find(s =>
  s.meaning?.includes('feedback') ||
  s.meaning?.includes('clarification') ||
  s.meaning?.includes('blockers') ||
  s.name.toLowerCase().includes('feedback')
);
```

